{"tid":2269666,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"維港頌揸三年蝕83萬","createTime":"2020-11-03T14:45:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-06T13:14:07.000Z","uid":73269,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6147acc5bd24823c9ef0efba48bbe6b96e957057","tid":2269666,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T14:45:34.000Z","msg":"長實新一代豪宅，都是要蝕讓。陸續三年額外印花稅(SSD)鬆綁的北角維港頌，繼4房單位慘蝕外，連帶一房單位都要蝕，連使費料蝕83萬元。入伙約一年的維港頌，中原地產林龍南表示，6座高層B室，實用面積432方呎，屬一房單位，向東北，望樓景。業主剛以1,160萬元將單位沽出，實用呎價26,852元。據悉原業主於2017年4月以1,187萬元買入單位，持貨3年，帳面蝕27萬元，單位貶值2%。若連同釐印費及佣金，料損手達83萬元。"},{"pid":"5a15b1ae639f911e5969b1f5744f1f4eaf9eb1a7","tid":2269666,"uid":9633,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T14:46:49.000Z","msg":"有人接<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7efc14a3d6274fa7951725f3c106aa9626b45fb","tid":2269666,"uid":39383,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a15b1ae639f911e5969b1f5744f1f4eaf9eb1a7","tid":2269666,"uid":9633,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T14:46:49.000Z","msg":"有人接<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T14:50:46.000Z","msg":"呢個真, 對後市好有信心"},{"pid":"7e4a4c0bc8ef6c092b129b4da129e35c99e6d076","tid":2269666,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T15:59:16.000Z","msg":"港島一樣死，bno"},{"pid":"e075c9251f952b4c5e737ce352fa4454a5e7f196","tid":2269666,"uid":329544,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7e4a4c0bc8ef6c092b129b4da129e35c99e6d076","tid":2269666,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T15:59:16.000Z","msg":"港島一樣死，bno"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T04:26:16.000Z","msg":"廿幾萬好少啫"},{"pid":"6e7e1950484b5e50a898acdaecd5a96446ac7821","tid":2269666,"uid":30868,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedB